       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CheckEvenOdd.
               
        ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.       
        INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  NUM      PIC 9(5).
       01  REM      PIC 9.
       01  Result   PIC 9(10).
       01  Rem2     pic 9(10).
       01  Rem3     pic 9(05).
       01  rem4     pic 9(02).
       01  result1   pic 9(10).
       01  result2   pic 9(10).
       01  result3   pic 9(10).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "Enter a number: " WITH NO ADVANCING.
           ACCEPT NUM.

           IF  REM = 0 THEN
            DISPLAY "The number is EVEN."
           ELSE
            DISPLAY "The number is ODD."
           END-IF.
              DISPLAY rem4 .
           STOP RUN.
           